{"tid":2454984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：拜登太軟弱 中國先可以咁串","createTime":"2021-03-20T16:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T04:47:16.000Z","uid":125168,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a3be10b985251a08cad943a74c8863e2f532d6c8","tid":2454984,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210320/OCKS2BODWBB2NJ2RPIE4ALLAHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FOCKS2BODWBB2NJ2RPIE4ALLAHA%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=42279604\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FOCKS2BODWBB2NJ2RPIE4ALLAHA%2F&h=ecb3f6fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210320/OCKS2BODWBB2NJ2RPIE4ALLAHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n中美會談｜蓬佩奧：中國知道拜登對華軟弱退縮 致整場會談可以咄咄逼人<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登上任後首場中美高層會談結束，雙方充滿火藥味兼分歧嚴重。雖然拜登讚揚國務卿布林肯的表現，但前任國務卿蓬佩奧受訪時，直言中國知道拜登對華軟弱，面對中方批評又採取退縮態度，導致對方整場會談都咄咄逼人。<br />\n<br />\n對無反擊感失望<br />\n<br />\n漢尼蒂問蓬佩奧如果他是會談代表會如何做，蓬佩奧指中方以黑人歧視問題批評美國民主是「不可理喻」，形容美國是民主世界的燈塔，中國這樣攻擊簡直是「瘋狂」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧直言會以武漢肺炎反擊：「我會反問他們對這個世界做了甚麼，武漢肺炎帶走了數以百萬計性命，數以十億計的財富，她們（美方）沒有以這種方式向對方反壓是不能接受的。」"},{"pid":"04eff07440f31b3651d29d25b6a8816eb3845f3e","tid":2454984,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4b04bd5d1b924e09d6bf691b52b47942ed737d","tid":2454984,"uid":227271,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"如果呀侵仲係到，支那邊敢咁放肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyb4ZPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnyb4ZPR.jpg&h=b8247158&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LyA9ruS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s